<br />Bregalad and Disch: You both are right on that,
<br />
<br />Disch: I can do your instructions to make it working, unless it won't work,
<br />
<br />Mottzilla: It is not the enemies. Just a reaction to removing the sprite zero code, I can put Disch's Idea into play. and By The Way, It is only affecting to the range where the status bar was handling sprite 0.</div>

